@mistercrunch - selecting timeranges by datepickers is an option but not really sexy;)
Within all analysis, time is always a fixed dimension, that's why most BI tools have already prebuild calenders that allow to group, filter, sort by this special dimension.

I think what would be a possible option - is like an filter sidebar that you can open and then make your time pick ;)

if you like I can make a quick mockup ;)

Best Philipp
